parameters: Would you like to view the event? New SNS Promotion Event
\nc<Facilitator>Those who have been dispatched, please gather over here!

\nc<Facilitator>Yes, thank you. Now, we will install a newly released app in
the store called "Sex Connect."

\nc<Saki>Ugh, that's an app name that doesn't make me want to install
it at all...

\bustMsgExpression[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(Yeah, yeah. I get it. If I don't work my butt off, there's
no comfort for me.)

\nc<Saki>(To think I'd even have to authenticate my succubus
registration card... Oh well, whatever.)

\nc<Facilitator>Ha ha. It seems everyone is a bit tired, perhaps because
it's morning.

\nc<Saki>(Is it because you're holding such a shady event this early
in the morning?)

\nc<Facilitator>However... please listen carefully from here on. To raise
everyone's motivation, we have prepared a special reward.

\nc<Facilitator>This event, held in commemoration of the release of "Sex
Connect," is somewhat like a game of hide and seek.

\nc<Facilitator>If the customers catch you, you will have sex with them
right then and there.

\nc<Facilitator>However, if you can survive without being caught for two
hours... we will pay a special reward to those who do.
\bustMsgExpression[1, 5]\nc<Saki>H-hold on, you're really going to give us that much?

\nc<Facilitator>We can't have you slacking off and disappointing the
customers. Please take this seriously.
\nc<Facilitator>However, you must not leave the event venue.

\bustMsgExpression[1, 0]\nc<Saki>(Wait. If I think about it, this means I might be able to
get by without working at all?)
\nc<Facilitator>Heheh. It seems like everyone's getting motivated...

\nc<Facilitator>Now, please upload a promotional post about the event along
with a selfie using the app you've just installed.
\nc<Facilitator>Once you're done, I'll check it personally.
\nc<Saki>Eh... what are you going to write?

\bustMsgExpression[2, 2]\nc<Senpai>With this, the customers will flock to you like dogs in
heat. Good luck, Saki.
\bustMsgExpression[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Waaaah... what kind of person does this...

\nc<Facilitator>Excellent. This is exactly the kind of post we've been
waiting for.

\nc<Facilitator>Saki-san, you can start right away. The customers will be
entering in 10 minutes.
\bustMsgExpression[1, 1]\nc<Saki>(Eh? There's less time than I thought!)
